00:18:39.860 --> 00:18:42.870
potential that takes into
account the centrifugal

00:18:42.870 --> 00:18:44.870
PROFESSOR: Perfect, but
let's use L equals zero.

00:18:44.870 --> 00:18:48.360
Then the centrifugal
