00:18:48.360 --> 00:18:49.490
Otherwise you are right.

00:18:49.490 --> 00:18:50.900
It's an effective potential.

00:18:50.900 --> 00:18:53.720
But let's talk about L
equals zero, S states.

00:18:53.720 --> 00:18:58.660
Then there is no correction
