00:20:08.610 --> 00:20:09.580
PROFESSOR: Exactly.

00:20:09.580 --> 00:20:13.630
In the three dimensional case
you have a wave function psi,

00:20:13.630 --> 00:20:17.860
but then you do a substitution
that the 1D Schrodinger

00:20:17.860 --> 00:20:20.710
equation is not for
