00:20:25.800 --> 00:20:27.760
So you transform to a
different function, which

00:20:27.760 --> 00:20:31.570
is one more power of R. And
the requirement because of this

00:20:31.570 --> 00:20:34.090
is that your radial
wave function

00:20:34.090 --> 00:20:36.450
of this one-dimensional
