00:47:13.220 --> 00:47:15.810
You can say it's an
uncontrolled approximation,

00:47:15.810 --> 00:47:18.260
but it's based on intuition.

00:47:18.260 --> 00:47:20.860
So the hope is that
we still capture

00:47:20.860 --> 00:47:25.014
the essence of super fluidity by
doing this major simplification

00:47:25.014 --> 00:47:25.805
of the Hamiltonian.

00:47:29.210 --> 00:47:31.580
So now I want to show you
