You still have products
of four operators.

00:49:03.460 --> 00:49:05.310
We want to get rid of it.

00:49:05.310 --> 00:49:09.560
But now we use a
mean field idea.

00:49:09.560 --> 00:49:12.530
We always get rid of
products of four operators

00:49:12.530 --> 00:49:15.070
by grabbing one or two
of them, and saying,

00:49:15.070 --> 00:49:16.520
"we don't look at
the operator, we

00:49:16.520 --> 00:49:19.340
look at the expectation value,
which is the mean field."

00:49:19.340 --> 00:49:22.430
So we want to make a
