00:50:57.600 --> 00:51:02.170
we drop quadratic terms,
which are fluctuation terms.

00:51:02.170 --> 00:51:04.960
And the moment we
have now, simply

00:51:04.960 --> 00:51:07.340
bi-linear product of operators.

00:51:07.340 --> 00:51:09.750
We do exactly the same
as we did with bosons,

00:51:09.750 --> 00:51:13.560
we transform to a new
set of operators, which

00:51:13.560 --> 00:51:15.910
is the Bogoliubov
Transformation.

00:51:15.910 --> 00:51:17.720
Of course, this time,
